comment: I feel like there isn't much a lab professor can do in coding... but he trys to explain the topics further. Him and his GTAs were really helpful in class and if you can't finish the lab then I would just go to the tutoring center. The lab final is worth 50% of your grade which is kind of crazy so there isn't much to work for until the end.
Hes a graduate teaching assistant, very nice. although the department is crappy. hes easy and lenient on things. you cant miss any lab days tho!
